{"tid":546116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港男盜公司3.8億　澳門4人涉助洗錢","createTime":"2018-01-31T08:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T11:21:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96734dc8e3d8ca85de77eb2db186f9c0b7d2b23e","tid":546116,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180131/20290981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F20290981&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=46f8c4c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F20290981&h=d46e870f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180131/20290981</a><br />\n<br />\n港男盜公司3.8億　澳門4人涉助洗錢<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】澳門司警偵破一宗涉香港的洗黑錢案，拘捕4名澳門居民，並扣押涉案值4,000萬元財物。案件源於香港一宗盜竊案，一名任職商船公司會計部的姓馬男子，以職務之便將3.8億元資金轉到個人賬戶，馬於2016年3月被港警拘捕。船公司去年初發現部份贓款轉移到澳門，在當地報案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180131/large/a1004a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180131%2Flarge%2Fa1004a.jpg&h=8b5f5d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被捕3男1女被控以清洗黑錢及贓物罪，移送檢察院偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前女友涉處理3,800萬<br />\n<br />\n司警指被捕4名澳門居民，主犯是32歲姓袁女子，她與姓馬港男曾是情侶，她的賬戶在2010至2016年間曾收到3,800萬港元匯款，並將當中2,400萬元轉至馬在澳門及香港的戶口。袁的賬戶亦出現多筆合共2,500萬元來歷不明的存款。她其後用相關資金買賣物業，又夥同父親、胞弟及現任男友等，收藏其懷疑使用贓款購買的大批名貴皮具、金飾、手錶等。<br />\n<br />\n司警扣押涉案人等用犯罪所得購買的兩幢物業、4輛名車。司警前日再到4人住所搜查，搜獲逾百名牌手袋、手錶、錢包、金飾及現金等，所扣押的犯罪得益約值4,000萬港元。涉案男女被控清洗黑錢及贓物罪，移送檢察院偵辦。司警無透露姓馬港男及船公司的資料。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"bf76fd3ce8000b4b8b26ec7c3906378d00eabf19","tid":546116,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"間船公司...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3a34c9a23a6237ce30a80666792073488ff84a","tid":546116,"uid":36152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf76fd3ce8000b4b8b26ec7c3906378d00eabf19","tid":546116,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"間船公司...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"紅公司？"},{"pid":"14e1ea6683bec59e1bc3208e25882480e2584b4c","tid":546116,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"咁公司拎唔拎得返個幾億"},{"pid":"cc1bc3ebaa26f1fb00b5a78acf44903145bc396c","tid":546116,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"3.8億要坐幾多碌"},{"pid":"6d1550f2ae8591b5183d08cee54a1247e405b57d","tid":546116,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}